p: I Sarah E. Seibert the deponent named in this the within summoned hereby enter my appearance in this cause and name any and all service of Complaint and summoned herein.
Done at Olympia Thurston County Washington Territory the 12h day of June A.D. 1871.
IN THE DISTRICT COURT of the Second Judicial District of the TERRITORY OF WASHINGTON.
John Seibert vs. Sarah E. Seibert
Filed this 25th day of May A..D. 1878

I hereby certify that I read the within summon and a copy of the complaint herein by delivering to and bringing with the within named defendant on the day of A.D. 18 in the county of a copy of said summons and a copy of said complaint. Dated this day of 18
